[
  {
    "text": "President Trump's trade",
    "start": 0.033,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "war with American allies.",
    "start": 1.134,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "Tariffs on imported goods",
    "start": 3.036,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "are now at their highest levels",
    "start": 4.437,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "since the Great Depression.",
    "start": 6.473,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Products from Mexico",
    "start": 8.775,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "and Canada are exempt from those duties",
    "start": 9.843,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "if and only if they comply with the U.S.",
    "start": 12.379,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Mexico-Canada Free Trade Agreement.",
    "start": 15.382,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Otherwise, Mexican imports face",
    "start": 17.584,
    "duration": 2.502
  },
  {
    "text": "25% tariffs,",
    "start": 20.086,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "while Canadian goods face 35%.",
    "start": 21.654,
    "duration": 3.037
  },
  {
    "text": "Joining us",
    "start": 25.058,
    "duration": 0.567
  },
  {
    "text": "now is the premier of Ontario Doug Ford.",
    "start": 25.625,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Premier Ford,",
    "start": 27.927,
    "duration": 0.601
  },
  {
    "text": "thanks so much for joining us.",
    "start": 28.528,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "As you know,",
    "start": 30.063,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "President Trump",
    "start": 30.53,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "negotiated the agreement",
    "start": 31.231,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "with Canada and Mexico",
    "start": 32.966,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "during his first term",
    "start": 34.2,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "to replace NAFTA, the North American",
    "start": 35.602,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "Free Trade Agreement.",
    "start": 37.67,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "You say",
    "start": 39.239,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "and now he could push suddenly",
    "start": 40.006,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "all of a sudden open up the Usmca.",
    "start": 41.674,
    "duration": 2.737
  },
  {
    "text": "What makes you think that?",
    "start": 44.411,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, you know, well, first of all,",
    "start": 47.914,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "I start off",
    "start": 49.916,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "every interview with saying",
    "start": 50.45,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "how much we love Americans,",
    "start": 51.451,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "how much we love the U.S.",
    "start": 52.786,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "and as I've said on this",
    "start": 54.421,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "show, many times,",
    "start": 55.422,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "that a tariff on Canada",
    "start": 56.856,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "is a tax on the American people.",
    "start": 58.158,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "And as you've seen the study from Yale,",
    "start": 60.36,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "it's going to cost Americans $2,400",
    "start": 63.096,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "manufacturing unemployment in the U.S..",
    "start": 66.466,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "there's over 37,000 people since April,",
    "start": 69.502,
    "duration": 3.17
  },
  {
    "text": "have lost their jobs.",
    "start": 73.473,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the lowest",
    "start": 74.607,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "rate in five years,",
    "start": 75.542,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's just not working.",
    "start": 77.544,
    "duration": 2.068
  },
  {
    "text": "let's let's create the American fortress.",
    "start": 79.612,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Two strongest countries in the world.",
    "start": 82.982,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "again, this is hurting",
    "start": 85.485,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "the American people,",
    "start": 87.12,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "as the rest of the countries,",
    "start": 88.688,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "including Canada,",
    "start": 90.123,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "is diversifying our trade.",
    "start": 91.591,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "We're seeing,",
    "start": 93.493,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "25% increase in trade",
    "start": 95.061,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "with European Union.",
    "start": 97.263,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "the UK is up by 30%.",
    "start": 99.032,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "So as we're diversifying in on shoring,",
    "start": 101.401,
    "duration": 2.969
  },
  {
    "text": "products, the American people are losing",
    "start": 104.437,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "their jobs.",
    "start": 106.773,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "What would",
    "start": 108.408,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "the impact be for Canada and for the U.S.",
    "start": 108.875,
    "duration": 3.237
  },
  {
    "text": "if if President Trump",
    "start": 112.112,
    "duration": 1.701
  },
  {
    "text": "pulled out of that agreement?",
    "start": 113.813,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it'd be unfortunate.",
    "start": 117.984,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "We we,",
    "start": 119.486,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "directly employ just Ontario alone,",
    "start": 120.553,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "9 million Americans.",
    "start": 122.755,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "And across the entire country of Canada",
    "start": 124.19,
    "duration": 2.569
  },
  {
    "text": "is probably closer",
    "start": 126.759,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "to 20 million Americans",
    "start": 127.56,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "rely on Canada for jobs, and vice versa.",
    "start": 129.462,
    "duration": 3.27
  },
  {
    "text": "We rely on, jobs.",
    "start": 132.932,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "with trade with the U.S.,",
    "start": 136.069,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "but it's just hurting both countries.",
    "start": 137.937,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "And as we're diversifying",
    "start": 140.573,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "and the rest of the world's diversifying,",
    "start": 142.709,
    "duration": 2.569
  },
  {
    "text": "on shoring products",
    "start": 145.278,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "that are typically made in the U.S.,",
    "start": 146.513,
    "duration": 2.769
  },
  {
    "text": "no matter if it's aluminum cans",
    "start": 149.282,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "or tins or, steel beams.",
    "start": 151.084,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "we're on trying everything.",
    "start": 154.354,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "we're very,",
    "start": 156.389,
    "duration": 0.534
  },
  {
    "text": "very concerned",
    "start": 156.923,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "with the actions",
    "start": 158.024,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "of the Trump administration.",
    "start": 158.858,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "And, you know, President Trump and",
    "start": 160.693,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "and Secretary Mack,",
    "start": 163.263,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "they're they're smart guys like,",
    "start": 164.697,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "they understand numbers.",
    "start": 166.399,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "And when you see",
    "start": 167.767,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "37,000 Americans have lost their jobs,",
    "start": 168.568,
    "duration": 3.337
  },
  {
    "text": "they can't pay the rent",
    "start": 171.905,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "or can't pay a mortgage,",
    "start": 173.373,
    "duration": 1.434
  },
  {
    "text": "put food on their table.",
    "start": 174.807,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "And this is just going to grow even more.",
    "start": 176.309,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "6.2 billion in tariff",
    "start": 178.111,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "related costs to the auto sector.",
    "start": 180.213,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's going to increase.",
    "start": 182.415,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "So the auto workers",
    "start": 184.017,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "are going to be losing their jobs.",
    "start": 185.051,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "So how is Canada,",
    "start": 187.42,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Premier Ford",
    "start": 189.122,
    "duration": 0.634
  },
  {
    "text": "preparing for that possibility now?",
    "start": 189.756,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Have you, warned your Prime Minister,",
    "start": 192.392,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Mark Carney, that Canada",
    "start": 194.194,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "needs to take action?",
    "start": 195.762,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "Absolutely.",
    "start": 199.299,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "And we're doing it as we speak right now.",
    "start": 200.133,
    "duration": 2.335
  },
  {
    "text": "We're on shoring,",
    "start": 202.468,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "unsure,",
    "start": 203.636,
    "duration": 0.501
  },
  {
    "text": "and manufacturing jobs",
    "start": 204.137,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "that typically are American jobs.",
    "start": 205.471,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "we we have a market here",
    "start": 208.474,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "that we can sustain it,",
    "start": 209.976,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "and we're lowering taxes.",
    "start": 211.578,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "We're making sure we're competitive",
    "start": 213.513,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "for companies",
    "start": 215.448,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "to come and invest in Canada.",
    "start": 216.182,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Ontario alone last year",
    "start": 219.419,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "attracted over $40 billion of investment,",
    "start": 220.887,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "creating more jobs, more opportunities.",
    "start": 223.923,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "I would much rather,",
    "start": 226.659,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "you know, work with our greatest,",
    "start": 228.261,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "ally and closest friend",
    "start": 230.163,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "and increase jobs in both countries,",
    "start": 232.232,
    "duration": 2.702
  },
  {
    "text": "and we can do that.",
    "start": 234.934,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "We'd be the two strongest nations",
    "start": 236.169,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "in the world economically.",
    "start": 237.837,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "that's that that's our goal.",
    "start": 239.839,
    "duration": 1.602
  },
  {
    "text": "But unfortunately, President",
    "start": 241.441,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump doesn't",
    "start": 243.243,
    "duration": 0.467
  },
  {
    "text": "want to go down that avenue.",
    "start": 243.71,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "He wants to hurt the American people.",
    "start": 244.978,
    "duration": 2.135
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's exactly what he's doing.",
    "start": 247.113,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you know when,",
    "start": 249.182,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "Prime Minister Carney of Canada is next",
    "start": 250.116,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "scheduled to speak with President Trump?",
    "start": 252.819,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd imagine over the next few days, Wolf.",
    "start": 256.756,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "But we're going to continue the dialog",
    "start": 259.892,
    "duration": 2.37
  },
  {
    "text": "and communication",
    "start": 262.262,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "to the best of our ability.",
    "start": 263.863,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, it's it's strange to me,",
    "start": 266.599,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump has repeatedly said",
    "start": 268.368,
    "duration": 1.701
  },
  {
    "text": "over these past several months",
    "start": 270.069,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "that he wants Canada,",
    "start": 271.704,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "our neighbor",
    "start": 273.106,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "in the North,",
    "start": 273.606,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "to become a 51st",
    "start": 274.407,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "state of the United States.",
    "start": 276.075,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "He hasn't said that, though, in a while.",
    "start": 277.644,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you still worry",
    "start": 279.946,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "about his rhetoric on that front?",
    "start": 280.813,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, I'm not I'm not worried about that",
    "start": 284.817,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "because that's never going to happen.",
    "start": 286.886,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll be your closest",
    "start": 288.221,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "ally and closest friend for forever,",
    "start": 289.055,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "as we have been for 200 years.",
    "start": 291.491,
    "duration": 2.402
  },
  {
    "text": "And we will outlast",
    "start": 293.893,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "the Trump administration",
    "start": 295.428,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "and will continue working",
    "start": 297.196,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "with our great American partners.",
    "start": 298.831,
    "duration": 2.403
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the general impression",
    "start": 301.234,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "of Trump in Canada?",
    "start": 302.435,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "He's probably the most",
    "start": 306.773,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "disliked politician",
    "start": 307.507,
    "duration": 1.067
  },
  {
    "text": "in the world, in Canada",
    "start": 308.574,
    "duration": 1.302
  },
  {
    "text": "because he's attacked his closest,",
    "start": 309.876,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "family member.",
    "start": 311.778,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's the way we look upon it.",
    "start": 312.512,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "And when I talk to the governors",
    "start": 314.314,
    "duration": 1.334
  },
  {
    "text": "and senators and Congress, people,",
    "start": 315.648,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "even Republicans totally disagree,",
    "start": 318.918,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "but they're too scared to",
    "start": 320.853,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "come out and say anything,",
    "start": 321.721,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "because the president will go after them.",
    "start": 323.69,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Outside of a few senators.",
    "start": 325.558,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "And I want to thank them for",
    "start": 326.926,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "for coming out",
    "start": 328.995,
    "duration": 0.767
  },
  {
    "text": "and staying",
    "start": 329.762,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "standing with not just American people,",
    "start": 330.863,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "but their closest friends and, allies,",
    "start": 332.899,
    "duration": 3.136
  },
  {
    "text": "which is Canada.",
    "start": 336.169,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "And again, we love the Americans.",
    "start": 337.47,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "It's unfortunate that President Trump",
    "start": 339.205,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "decided to go down this road.",
    "start": 341.04,
    "duration": 2.469
  },
  {
    "text": "And just to be, totally transparent,",
    "start": 343.509,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "as someone who grew up on the US",
    "start": 345.778,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Canada border in beautiful Buffalo,",
    "start": 347.58,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "New York, I love Canada as well.",
    "start": 349.415,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "I love the Canadians",
    "start": 350.95,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "and always have,",
    "start": 352.018,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "the Ontario Premier, Doug Ford, as usual.",
    "start": 353.319,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks so much for joining us.",
    "start": 355.521,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 357.357,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "CNN business and politics",
    "start": 358.157,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "correspondent Vanessa York",
    "start": 359.792,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "is joining us from New York. Right now.",
    "start": 361.527,
    "duration": 2.203
  },
  {
    "text": "Vanessa, countries",
    "start": 363.73,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "are paying these new tariffs.",
    "start": 364.63,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "What kinds of products",
    "start": 366.065,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "are we really talking about?",
    "start": 367.533,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah.",
    "start": 369.869,
    "duration": 0.234
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, Wolf,",
    "start": 370.103,
    "duration": 0.4
  },
  {
    "text": "these are historic tariff levels",
    "start": 370.503,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "not seen in nearly a century.",
    "start": 372.271,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "We have not seen tariffs at these rates",
    "start": 374.04,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "since the 1930s.",
    "start": 375.842,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "And following",
    "start": 377.31,
    "duration": 0.6
  },
  {
    "text": "that was the Great Depression.",
    "start": 377.91,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "And all countries are being hit.",
    "start": 379.879,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "The minimum is 10%,",
    "start": 381.781,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "but then it's ratcheted up",
    "start": 383.316,
    "duration": 1.134
  },
  {
    "text": "to 50% for some countries.",
    "start": 384.45,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "This is President Trump's big bet.",
    "start": 386.652,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "He believes that he's going to shrink",
    "start": 388.921,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "trade deficits with other countries,",
    "start": 390.69,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "and believe that he's",
    "start": 392.592,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "going to move manufacturing",
    "start": 393.459,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "to the United States.",
    "start": 395.261,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "Here are some of the countries",
    "start": 396.529,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "that are impacted.",
    "start": 397.53,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at that high rate for Brazil,",
    "start": 398.498,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Switzerland, 39%.",
    "start": 400.5,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "That's actually higher",
    "start": 402.468,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "than the initial tariff of 31%",
    "start": 403.302,
    "duration": 2.837
  },
  {
    "text": "that was announced on Liberation Day.",
    "start": 406.139,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "You have India 25%.",
    "start": 408.007,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "Trump has threatened",
    "start": 410.042,
    "duration": 0.701
  },
  {
    "text": "to move that up to 50%.",
    "start": 410.743,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Vietnam, Cambodia,",
    "start": 412.578,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "other East",
    "start": 413.913,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Asian countries at 20% 19%",
    "start": 414.58,
    "duration": 2.937
  },
  {
    "text": "and the European Union",
    "start": 417.517,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "a major trading partner.",
    "start": 418.751,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "Wolf, sitting at 15%.",
    "start": 420.186,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "They actually negotiated",
    "start": 421.954,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "that tariff level",
    "start": 423.689,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "as Trump",
    "start": 424.857,
    "duration": 0.568
  },
  {
    "text": "was trying to bring that even higher.",
    "start": 425.425,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "But a significant historic day",
    "start": 427.16,
    "duration": 2.135
  },
  {
    "text": "as nearly all countries",
    "start": 429.295,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "now hit with historic tariff levels.",
    "start": 430.73,
    "duration": 2.636
  },
  {
    "text": "Vanessa, how much is this going to cost?",
    "start": 433.366,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Average Americans?",
    "start": 435.234,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, well,",
    "start": 437.27,
    "duration": 0.367
  },
  {
    "text": "this is going to hit a lot of products",
    "start": 437.637,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "that we Americans love to buy",
    "start": 439.605,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "computers, electronics",
    "start": 441.441,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "coming in from countries",
    "start": 443.309,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "like China, Vietnam,",
    "start": 444.51,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Malaysia being hit with 30,",
    "start": 446.712,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "20, 19% tariffs,",
    "start": 448.514,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "clothing and shoes",
    "start": 450.55,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "coming in from China, Vietnam,",
    "start": 451.584,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "India",
    "start": 453.052,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "going to be hit with 3,020% 25 tariffs.",
    "start": 453.953,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Watch is now on the list",
    "start": 457.223,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "because of Americans",
    "start": 458.524,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "love for Swiss watches.",
    "start": 459.392,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "That's going to be tariff",
    "start": 461.16,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "to 39% alcohol",
    "start": 462.028,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "coming in from the European Union.",
    "start": 463.796,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "Countries like France and Italy.",
    "start": 465.832,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "That's wine",
    "start": 468.201,
    "duration": 0.867
  },
  {
    "text": "and spirits going to be tariff to 15%",
    "start": 469.068,
    "duration": 2.669
  },
  {
    "text": "and toys being tariff",
    "start": 471.737,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "at 30 to 20%, coming in from China",
    "start": 473.105,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "and Vietnam.",
    "start": 476.108,
    "duration": 1.469
  },
  {
    "text": "There are many, many estimates",
    "start": 477.577,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "to suggest what this may cost",
    "start": 479.312,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "American families.",
    "start": 480.813,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "The most recent estimate that we have",
    "start": 481.914,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "is from the Yale Budget Lab",
    "start": 483.85,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "just this month, projecting that",
    "start": 485.618,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "because of all of these tariffs,",
    "start": 487.253,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "if they stay in effect, it's",
    "start": 489.021,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "going to cost the average family $2,400",
    "start": 490.389,
    "duration": 3.771
  },
  {
    "text": "a year.",
    "start": 494.16,
    "duration": 0.801
  },
  {
    "text": "Obviously,",
    "start": 494.961,
    "duration": 0.734
  },
  {
    "text": "that is significant as Americans",
    "start": 495.695,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "we know are worried about these tariffs,",
    "start": 497.663,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "worried about their finances,",
    "start": 499.799,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "worried about inflation.",
    "start": 501.4,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "That is a significant hit to the average",
    "start": 503.035,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "American family, Wolf.",
    "start": 505.004,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "Indeed it is hard to see your kids.",
    "start": 506.372,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you very, very much.",
    "start": 508.174,
    "duration": 1.301
  }
]